{"tid":303128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[英國研究]愛賴床的人聰明有創意","createTime":"2017-06-30T02:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T16:14:45.000Z","uid":105567,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60a4f86f617c0501039d3cbc423c51dc54665171","tid":303128,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1846454/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1846454%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=jdE0CXUA4ZDiSTzF1B2RBgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=fbc9ee60\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1846454/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n每朝返工上學前，鬧鐘無情地響起的瞬間，相信大家都經過苦苦的爭扎。不只設了數個鬧鐘，還要按無數次的「Snooze」鬧鐘延遲鍵，讓自己再睡多10分鐘的回籠覺。<br />\n<br />\n不過現在愛賴床的人不用感到內疚了﹗英國有研究指，愛賴床的人其實更聰明、更開心、更有創造力。<br />\n<br />\n英國南安普敦大學（University of South Hampton）發表的研究報告「為什麼夜貓子更加聰明」（Why Night Owls Are More Intelligent）。夜貓子是指晚上11點後睡覺，8點多起床的人。而他們一般有更高的收入及更舒適的生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n是次研究共招募1,229名男女進行調查，了解他們的睡眠模式與社會經濟之間的關係。研究員Satoshi Kanazawa及Kaja Perina認為，使用鬧鐘延遲鍵「Snooze」的人，大多屬晚睡一族，其生活較不規律：<br />\n<br />\n這種人懂得按自己的步行走，懂得聆聽身體需求，懂得自我解決問題，更容易適應世界的變化。於性格上一般更有創造力與獨立能力，也更為聰明，活得更開心。<br />\n另外，研究亦發現女性比男性需要多20分鐘睡眠，事關女性要兼顧的日常事情較男性多。可是，這不代表我們要花更多時間睡覺，因為每天睡超過12小時或以上的人，已被證證有較高的死亡風險。"},{"pid":"d699753dbe36e6742087db3abe20075ba05cbbec","tid":303128,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"作倒呢D野幫自己辯護,的確幾有創意"},{"pid":"6c25ecf1f3d8f61f18473b8f2a330c3df9f56923","tid":303128,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:28:39.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢青"},{"pid":"c3bab55ec2696146d1b1a3ed4ac28d497a16bd2f","tid":303128,"uid":73054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"記住係講緊8點幾先起身"},{"pid":"84576289483830d8b131922ab189e0e0287fdb14","tid":303128,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"英國研究，完"},{"pid":"2fa45489d4a7502864b9a2e75ccae5cd35182d0b","tid":303128,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"e0ae9c87410c3b8c7dad5018104ef67ac0677d5c","tid":303128,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾，喺你地賴緊床嘅時候早起嘅人已經做咗一日最麻煩嘅工作<br />\n利申每日5點半起身"},{"pid":"d5437f4e798a089c941bb0845e58f04a0e587c99","tid":303128,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"因為廢人先要做奴隸 <br />\n好似係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓上啲撚樣酸到呢"},{"pid":"aeb98dde6b90cfcb48a1237082aaa742c0996d2d","tid":303128,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534d22f92b9933b6c7ad6dc6df21440965b67ef0","tid":303128,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"我只係唔夠訓咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0b261e8c3f693bf71f87bc63fe0b681ca00a03","tid":303128,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"我今日較鬧鐘0845 最後我典到0930先起身<br />\n遲硬到<br />\n我諗左好多唔到嘅借口 算唔算係創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a59781bfa201118f44b76b687c48022ed986291","tid":303128,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}